  "texts": [
    "AdvancedIF, we further advance the difficulty of explicit user instruction by targeting user prompts with 6+ instructions, with a combination of tone, format, style, structure, length, negative constraints, spelling, and inter-conditional instructions.",
    "• Multi-Turn Carried Context Instruction Following: The ability to follow instructions carried from the previous conversation context.",
    "It can be the general context setting at the beginning of the conversation, details scattered throughout the chat flow, back-and-forth content editing, and so on.",
    "• System Prompt Steerability: The ability to follow instructions in the system prompt.",
    "Constraints in the system prompt include the response style, safety, different product context settings, e.g., voice and tool-use specifications."
  ],
